<title>sạmḥny yạ sydy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 sạmḥny yạ sydy ạ̉nạ kẖạṭy ậty bṣlạty wṭlbạty
 fhl stgẖfr ly ạldẖnwb lmsẗ yd ạlrb qwyẗ tṣnʿ
 ạlạ̉ʿmạl tḥqqhạ sryʿaⁿạ gẖnyaⁿạ tḥml ạljbạl
 ạ̹dẖaⁿạ ql ly lmạdẖạ ạ̉nt tfʿl kl hdẖạ tḥtml ʿny yạrby
 hdẖạ ạlʿnạʾ tmsẖy mʿy wkạ̉n kẖl ly tsyr wykạ̉n
 ẓly qbl ạ̉n tsẖʿr btʿby tʿṭy ạldwạʾ
 ạ̹nt ạlgẖạfr ạlrḥym yạrby kẖdny lyk wlḥḍnk
 ạldạfỷ flmạdẖạ yạrby ạfʿl kl hdẖạ bk wạ̹nt
 bsʿh ṣdrk tqmyny</lyrics>
